description: OFFER DEADLINE OF 6PM on Monday 5/5!! THOMAS PARK — PRIVATE YARD, PRIME LOCATION! Snag this first-floor, pet-friendly condo in one of Southie’s hottest spots! Wide open layout, soaring 9+ foot ceilings, crown molding, and a huge bay window flooding the space with sunlight. The oversized eat-in kitchen is a showstopper — granite counters, stainless steel appliances, custom backsplash — ready for your next dinner party. The primary bedroom has two closets and a ceiling fan to keep things cool. The second bedroom is perfect for a nursery, home office, or guest room. Best part? Your own private, fully fenced yard with a deck and patio — serious city living upgrade. Plus, deeded storage and laundry downstairs. Tucked away on a quiet one-way street, but seconds to Broadway’s best bars, restaurants, shops, and the 1st open house = first chance to grab it. Places like this don’t sit.
